<item>
            <title>[JOHNZON-144] Using a @JohnzonConverter with Jsonb leads to an Exception</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JOHNZON-144</link>
                <project id="12315523" key="JOHNZON">Johnzon</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Converting a class which has a @JohnzonConverter annotation via Jsonb leads to a ClassCast exception:&lt;/p&gt;

