&lt;p&gt;In older Johnzon version the Converter simply got ignored. &lt;br/&gt;
We now try to pick up the Converter but seem to mess up this part due to our work on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JOHNZON-77&quot; title=&quot;support ObjectConverter in @JohnzonConverter&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JOHNZON-77&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;JOHNZON-77&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
